summary: Mr Ramlal has called ITC multiple times regarding issues with their service, but has not received any resolution. He is frustrated and would like a status update on his complaints. The agent, Monika, checks his record and confirms that he has three active complaints. Ramlal details the issues with each complaint, including a missing coupon, an unfulfilled request for a biscuit with the complaint number 60608 23568, and an old complaint of an open. Monika offers to connect him with the relevant department, but he requests that she personally look into the matter and provide him with updates. She assures him that she will prioritize his case and inform the team to resolve his issues as soon as possible.
